<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Event Update Notification</h1>
  <p>
    Hello <%= @customer.name || @customer.email %>,
  </p>
  <p>
    We're writing to inform you that an event you've booked tickets for has been updated:
  </p>
  
  <h2>Event Details:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Event:</strong> <%= @event.title %></li>
    <li><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @event.date.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></li>
    <li><strong>Venue:</strong> <%= @event.venue %></li>
    <li><strong>Your Ticket:</strong> <%= @ticket.ticket_type %></li>
    <li><strong>Quantity:</strong> <%= @booking.quantity %></li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>Changes Made:</h2>
  <ul>
    <% @changes.each do |field, value| %>
      <li><strong><%= field.capitalize %>:</strong> <%= value[1] %> (was: <%= value[0] %>)</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
  
  <p>If you have any questions regarding these changes, please contact us.</p>
  <p>Thank you for your understanding!</p>
</body>
</html>